WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:18.620
If he doesn't wake up within an hour, he never will.

2
00:00:18.620 --> 00:00:19.620
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:25.589
Augusta, I used to tell you something.

4
00:00:25.589 --> 00:00:27.589
He weaved all of this. It's true.

5
00:00:27.589 --> 00:00:33.159
And I know at times you felt in prison just being his lover.

6
00:00:33.159 --> 00:00:38.829
But for the past 15 years, he'd entrapped himself.

7
00:00:38.829 --> 00:00:44.479
Just for choosing to be with you.

8
00:00:44.479 --> 00:00:45.479
I'm sorry.

9
00:00:45.479 --> 00:00:52.729
Maybe this contract is our failure.

